5
00:00:32,870 --> 00:00:38,702
♪Storming the heights,
who dares compete♪

6
00:00:39,360 --> 00:00:45,459
♪Sword in hand, he's unstoppable♪

7
00:00:45,568 --> 00:00:50,144
